title: Quick Creamy Prawn Rigatoni with Zesty Herby Sprinkle and Courgette
description: The delicious creaminess of crème fraîche makes it the perfect thing to use in pasta sauces like this one. Chef Lizzie has kept things light and fresh using ingredients like juicy prawns, parsley, courgette and lemon for a dish that won’t disappoint.
